# Short-form content generator

Read root `AGENTS.md` at session start. Use `docs/` for detail — do not load all docs into context.

## Priorities

1. Minimal, correct diffs scoped to the task
2. Match existing repo patterns before introducing new ones
3. Update `docs/workflow/current-tasks.md` when starting or finishing agent work
4. Record architectural choices in `docs/adr/`

## Commands

Detect package manager from lockfile. Do not assume npm if another lockfile exists.

## Never

- Commit secrets or `.env` files
- Interpolate untrusted input into shell/SQL
- Commit unless the user explicitly asks

